solutions.content:
Recurse to the tail of the list.

On the way back up, return a tuple: ```(nextValueToMultiply, accumulatedValue)```

<< 1 is a binary left shift, 

```
public int GetDecimalValue(ListNode head)
{
	if (head == null) return 0;

	(int nextMult, int accumulatedValue) GetInternal(ListNode current)
	{
		if(current.next == null)
		{
			return (1 << 1, current.val);
		}

		var (nextMult, accumulatedValue) = GetInternal(current.next);

		return (nextMult << 1, accumulatedValue + current.val * nextMult);
	}

	return GetInternal(head).accumulatedValue;
}
```

